Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.footm.informationservice.api.Player

  • public class Player
extends Object
    The class Player is a JavaBean objects used to serialize and deserialize JSON request and response object by Jackson. This object contains only the main attribute(Basic) of the player
    Author:
    Rinor Sefa, Lundrim Azemi
